The paper deals with Deep Face Recognition (DFR) systems, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of deep neural networks (cs.LG) and convolutional neural networks (cs.MM) for face identification. The paper also mentions modifying an existing model (Deep-ID) for multi-view facial images, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
